{"tid":2490393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"花旗宣布將退出中國大陸零售銀行業務","createTime":"2021-04-15T14:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T06:54:15.000Z","uid":358086,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7d04dde35d791edd2ca62820988338886a064317","tid":2490393,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRhEp1aBt3cmCeFqqKxmEnBcnV2kbCJPkqcZmxwKo2syp?filename=scMPVVT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscMPVVT.png&h=bf48c43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彭博資訊報導，花旗集團計劃退出包括台灣在內的亞洲、歐洲、中東及北非等13國市場的零售銀行業務。<br />\n<br />\n花旗15日說，將退出在澳洲、巴林、<span class=\"red\">中國大陸</span>、印度、印尼、南韓、馬來西亞、菲律賓、台灣、泰國、越南、波蘭及俄羅斯的消費者特許經營。該公司將繼續在這些市場提供商品給機構客戶群，包括私人銀行、現金管理部門，以及投資銀行和交易事業等。<br />\n<br />\n根據花旗發表的聲明，該銀行將改從位於新加坡、香港、阿拉伯聯合大公國及倫敦等四個財富中心經營兩地區的消費者銀行業務。這項措施是花旗執行長芙瑞瑟（Jane Fraser）上個月對公司策略檢討的一環。芙瑞瑟在聲明說：「這使我們能透過這些重要的樞紐攫取強勁成長及財富管理事業所提供的誘人報酬。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/5391365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F5391365&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwLktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=421c2180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/5391365</a>"},{"pid":"422a53178e0d12e181a2bc5279463323143477eb","tid":2490393,"uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:23:17.000Z","msg":"人生太短出手要更大"},{"pid":"31ab1cd6f74e90a7582c4ce80b058ed167f3eae0","tid":2490393,"uid":284855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"居然唔包香港? 係咪搞分裂国家?"},{"pid":"a37c01992ec84e1f6b73fb8d5032f1d284ee1252","tid":2490393,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"酒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784323e4cd